<![CDATA[<p class="BodyCopy">I am pleased that you have accepted a conditional position to
act as a Support Worker this summer on NCS with the Challenge.</p>

<p class="BodyCopy">As part of the conditions we need to match you with a young
person. In order to do this I need to send you anonymised, sensitive
information about the them. As you are not yet contractually employed by The
Challenge we will need you to sign a confidentiality agreement before we can
send this information to you. You will not be able to be considered for a match
with a young person without this agreement returned.</p>

<p class="BodyCopy">I would be grateful if you would print, read and return a scanned signed copy of the attached agreement no later than <b>7 days </b>from the date noted above. A scanned copy with your
signature fulfils the requirements. Please ensure the file is less than 5 MB otherwise we will not be able to use the file.</p>

<p class="BodyCopy">Please do not hesitate to call if there is anything you would
like to clarify.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="BodyCopy"><br></p><p class="BodyCopy">Warm Regards,</p><div><div>Sherry Kimball</div><div>Senior Staffing Associate for Support Workers</div><div>The Challenge</div><div>London Waterloo Office</div><div>sherry.kimball@the-challenge.org</div><div>07785 623400</div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;">0203 6918723</span></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
