<![CDATA[<h1 style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ff0000" size="5">Support Worker Confidentiality Agreement</font></h1>

<p class="BodyCopy" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><b>Confidentiality &amp;
Data Protection</b></p>

<p class="BodyCopy" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;">You acknowledge that in the course of your conditional hiring
You will have access to confidential information. You will not disclose or use
or cause to be disclosed or used, at any time during or subsequent to this
agreement, any secret or confidential information of TCN or any of its
participants except as required by TCN in the connection with your performance
or as required by law.</p>

<p class="BodyCopy" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;">For the purpose of the Data Protection Act 1998 (“DPA 1998”)
You consent to the processing of all or any personal data relevant to their
engagement by TCN. Processing includes but is not limited to obtaining,
recording, using and holding data.</p>

